ch is called an Adaptive Boosting Support Vector Machines (AB-SVM)\nmethod. Experimental results show that the proposed AB-SVM method achieves a\nsatisfied result with more than 92% classification accuracy on average.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2015 16:23:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2015 08:28:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-29"}
